---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Our Team
metaTitle: "Meet the Team | Azalea Estates Fayetteville, GA"
description: "Meet the caring professionals behind Azalea Estates in Fayetteville, GA. Long-tenured staff with deep experience in senior care — many serving residents and families for years."
eyebrow: The People Behind the Care
pageIntro: "Long-tenured, deeply experienced, and genuinely passionate about the seniors they serve — that's our team."
eleventyComputed:
  pageHero: "{{ images.residentsLaughing }}"
permalink: /team/
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import icon %}

<!-- INTRO -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Who We Are</span>
        <h2>Familiar faces, trusted relationships.</h2>
        <p class="lead">At Azalea Estates, staff tenure is one of our most meaningful metrics. Many of our team members have worked here for years, some for more than a decade, because they genuinely love what they do.</p>
        <p>When a resident sees the same faces at breakfast, the same nurses at evening check-in, and the same activity director every morning, something important happens: they feel at home. That continuity of care is not accidental. We hire for it, train for it, and measure our success by it.</p>
        <p>Our team holds appropriate professional qualifications across all disciplines and fosters a collaborative culture that keeps residents at the center of every decision. Meeting them is one of the best parts of a campus visit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.communityExterior }}" alt="The warm, welcoming entrance of Azalea Estates in Fayetteville" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TEAM GRID -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Key Team Members</span>
      <h2>Get to know the Azalea team.</h2>
      <p>These are the professionals who run Azalea Estates day-to-day, and who your family will get to know over time.</p>
    </div>

    {%- set members = [
      { name: "Holly Woods",       title: "Executive Director",            since: 2016, icon: "shield",   photo: "/assets/images/Holly-Woods-scaled.jpg",              desc: "Holly oversees all operations at Azalea Estates, setting the tone for the warmth and professionalism residents and families experience every day on campus." },
      { name: "Mirna Coeur",       title: "Community Relations Counselor", since: 2014, icon: "users",    photo: "/assets/images/Mirna-Coeur.jpg",                     desc: "Mirna is typically the first person families speak with when exploring our community. She guides prospective residents and their loved ones through the decision process with patience, honesty, and genuine care." },
      { name: "Asha Faison",       title: "Resident Care Director",        since: 2022, icon: "heart",    photo: "/assets/images/Asha-Faison.jpg",                     desc: "Asha oversees all clinical care at the community, coordinating individualized care plans with physicians, families, and our nursing team to ensure every resident receives exactly the support they need." },
      { name: "Shameka Clark",     title: "Wellness Director",             since: 2021, icon: "dumbbell", photo: "/assets/images/Shameka-Clark-1024x1024.jpg",         desc: "With a BS in Exercise Physiology, Shameka leads our 3,000 sq. ft. wellness center, the heated saltwater pool program, our Parkinson's exercise regimen, and all individual fitness assessments." },
      { name: "Stacey Kennedy",    title: "Activities Assistant",          since: 2023, icon: "leaf",     photo: "/assets/images/Stacey-Kennedy--1024x1024.jpg",       desc: "Stacey works closely with our Activities Director to build and deliver the daily calendar of events that makes life at Azalea Estates so vibrant, from morning exercises to evening entertainment." },
      { name: "Bobbie Barczynski", title: "Kitchen Manager",               since: 1999, icon: "utensils", photo: "/assets/images/Bobbie-Barczynski-1024x1024.jpg",    desc: "Bobbie knows her residents' preferences by heart and takes real pride in every meal she puts on the table. Over 27 years in the same kitchen, she's more family than staff." },
      { name: "Sandy Zimmermann",  title: "Business Office Manager",       since: 2020, icon: "shield",   photo: "/assets/images/Sandy-Zimmermann-1024x1024.jpg",     desc: "Sandy handles admissions paperwork, billing, long-term care insurance coordination, and all the behind-the-scenes work that keeps families informed and move-ins running smoothly." },
      { name: "Harold Hardaway",   title: "Maintenance Director",          since: 2006, icon: "home",     photo: "/assets/images/Harold-Hardaway-1024x1024.jpg",      desc: "Harold has two decades of history with every corner of our building. Residents know him by name and count on him to respond quickly and take care of things right." },
      { name: "Marty Schilling",   title: "Maintenance Assistant",         since: 2019, icon: "home",     photo: "/assets/images/Marty-Schilling-1024x1024.jpg",      desc: "Marty supports Harold in keeping every corner of campus clean, safe, and well-maintained. He's known for his warm manner and quick turnaround on resident requests." },
      { name: "Sandra Zabala",     title: "Weekend Manager",               since: 2001, icon: "clock",    photo: "/assets/images/Sandra-Zabala-1024x1024.jpg",        desc: "Sandra ensures the weekend experience at Azalea Estates is every bit as attentive and well-run as weekdays. Residents and families count on her for the consistency and calm she brings every Saturday and Sunday." },
      { name: "Tony Hardy",        title: "Transportation Manager",        since: 2022, icon: "car",      photo: "/assets/images/Tony-Hardy-1024x1024.jpg",           desc: "Tony coordinates our courtesy transportation program, making sure residents get to medical appointments, shopping trips, and errands safely and on time." }
    ] -%}

    <div class="feature-grid feature-grid--4">
      {% for member in members %}
      <article class="team-card reveal">
        <div class="team-card__photo">
          <img src="{{ member.photo }}" alt="{{ member.name }}, {{ member.title }} at Azalea Estates" loading="lazy">
          {# Icon badge — kept as a thematic decor accent on the photo #}
          <div class="team-card__badge" aria-hidden="true">
            {{ icon(member.icon, 15) }}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card__body">
          <h3>{{ member.name }}</h3>
          <span class="team-card__title">{{ member.title }}</span>
          <span class="team-card__tenure">With us since {{ member.since }}</span>
          <p>{{ member.desc }}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES SECTION -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">What Unites Us</span>
      <h2>A team built around residents, not routines.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <h3>Years of Tenure</h3>
        <p>Long-tenured staff means residents see the same familiar faces year after year. Trust is built one consistent interaction at a time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <h3>Professional Credentials</h3>
        <p>From our licensed RN and LPN nursing team to our degreed Wellness Director, our staff carries the qualifications the people in our care deserve.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <h3>Collaborative Culture</h3>
        <p>Our team works together across every department: care, dining, wellness, and activities. Nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <h3>Genuine Passion</h3>
        <p>People don&rsquo;t stay in senior care for the paycheck. Our team is here because they want to make a real difference in someone&rsquo;s daily life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
<section class="testimonial">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonial__inner reveal">
      <span class="testimonial__mark">&ldquo;</span>
      <p class="testimonial__quote">What struck us most was how many staff members had been here for five, eight, even twelve years. When you&rsquo;re placing a parent, that kind of stability matters more than any brochure.</p>
      <p class="testimonial__attribution"><strong>The Morrison Family</strong> &middot; Daughter of a resident</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

